Gunmen have abducted female students of the Federal College of Forestry Mechanism in the Mando area of ​​Kaduna. According to the BBC, a witness said half of the female students were taken, but not a single male was abducted.  Commissioner for Internal Security and Home Affairs, Samuel Aruwan, has confirmed the incident, saying an investigation is ongoing.



